* Dinobot closed the doors behind Tavatron and himself, there was much to do 
before the battle occurred.
He looked at Tigerhawk as he typed like mad on the ship's computers but 
thought that it was typical since the Predacons could attack any moment, he 
sighed and put a hand on his stomach as he felt it growl.
Dinobot thought that it would be wise to eat something then see if he could 
find time to rest.
( 1/2 a mega-cycle later...)
Dinobot sat down at a computer desk in in a small room off to the side of 
the bridge, a trey of food off to the side. There was much to know before he 
could relax and start on his meal.*

" Computer, show record of the most current Predacon activity."

* A computer screen in front of him came to life and soon became full of the 
most current Predacon activities, mainly the events which had occurred 
within the last few solar-cycles.
Dinobot looked over the records carefully, wars could be won if one knew 
their enemies well.*
